      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 22:29:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽蒙特股价下跌，因盈利低于预期削弱利润激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/newmont-posts-biggest-quarterly-profit-since-2019-on-gold-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场消化了令人失望的盈利结果后，纽蒙特公司 (Newmont Corp.) 的股价下跌，这表明这家全球最大的黄金生产商正努力控制其矿山的成本并利用金价飙升的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-23/newmont-posts-biggest-quarterly-profit-since-2019-on-gold-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 20:35:18 GMT</pubDate>
